    "description": {
      "value": "<p><strong>Role:</strong> Defender. You are very tough and have the exceptional ability to contain enemies in melee</p>\n<p><strong>Power Source:</strong> Martial. You have become a master of combat through endless hours of practice, determination, and your own sheer physical toughness.</p>\n<p><strong>Key Abilities:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Strength</li>\n<li>Dexterity</li>\n<li>Wisdom</li>\n<li>Constitution</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Armour Proficiencies:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>@UUID[Compendium.dnd4e.equipmentPack.Item.GwsMGFG3ogxFrvmJ]{Cloth armor (basic clothing)}</li>\n<li>@UUID[Compendium.dnd4e.equipmentPack.Item.lnYMh2YvKedWTpCt]{Leather armor}</li>\n<li>@UUID[Compendium.dnd4e.equipmentPack.Item.kVD04UqK9Yx6GeRA]{Hide armor}</li>\n<li>@UUID[Compendium.dnd4e.equipmentPack.Item.LEPCRMtCimzvXr25]{Chainmail}</li>\n<li>@UUID[Compendium.dnd4e.equipmentPack.Item.cCQ2LmmlBGYPf2KB]{Scale armor}</li>\n<li>@UUID[Compendium.dnd4e.equipmentPack.Item.7OaRnh5zUoThmChj]{Light Shield}</li>\n<li>@UUID[Compendium.dnd4e.equipmentPack.Item.bWxWgBpsJHWeTeIU]{Heavy Shield}</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Weapon Proficiencies:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>@Compendium[dnd4e.srd_rules.4vItzLTePIjC1MbI]{Simple Melee Weapons}</li>\n<li>@Compendium[dnd4e.srd_rules.oRfaQkmDSxWMx5Ln]{Military Melee Weapons}</li>\n<li>@Compendium[dnd4e.srd_rules.XKgEgbttyURcvqns]{Simple Ranged Weapons}</li>\n<li>@Compendium[dnd4e.srd_rules.xttyKhBLZaMknOGm]{Military Ranged Weapons}</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Bonus to Defences:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>+2 Fort&nbsp;</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Hit Points at 1st Level:</strong>&nbsp;[[15]] + Con Score</p>\n<p><strong>Hit Points </strong><strong>per Level Gained: </strong>[[6]]</p>\n<p><strong>Base </strong><strong>Healing</strong><strong>&nbsp;Surges per Day: </strong>[[9]] + Con Mod</p>\n<p><strong>Skill Training:</strong> Choose three from the following list:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Athletics (Str)</li>\n<li>Endurance (Con)</li>\n<li>Healing (Wis)</li>\n<li>Intimidate (Cha)</li>\n<li>Streetwise (Cha)</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Class Features:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>@UUID[Compendium.dnd4e.featuresPack.Item.7ADj4OuVS1704rgz]{Fighter Challenge}</li>\n<li>@UUID[Compendium.dnd4e.featuresPack.Item.IaRTeKkrO7uREL1v]{Fighter Superiority}</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Choose one of the following Combat Weapon Talent:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>@UUID[Compendium.dnd4e.featuresPack.Item.kgR65PH0ZQwSU3Lw]{Combat Weapon Talent - One Handed}</li>\n<li>@UUID[Compendium.dnd4e.featuresPack.Item.4OewAM0fKxcFbS8k]{Combat Weapon Talent - Two Handed}</li>\n</ul>",
